give(uint256,address).details: Give the position ownership to a destination address

params._destination: The destination to be a new owner of the position

importPosition(address,uint256).details: Import lockedCollateral and debtShare from the source address to the PositionHandler owned by the PositionManager. The source address must allow position's owner to do so.

params._source: The source PositionHandler to be moved to this PositionManager

moveCollateral(bytes32,uint256,address,u.details: Transfer wad amount of any type of collateral (collateralPoolId) from the positionHandler address to the destination address This function has the purpose to take away collateral from the system that doesn't correspond to the position but was sent there wrongly

params._positionId: The position id to move collateral from

params._data: The extra data for the adapter
params._positionId: The position id to move collateral from
params._wad: The amount in wad to be moved

movePosition(uint256,uint256).details: Move position's lockedCollateral and debtShare from the source PositionHandler to the destination PositionHandler
